mele unar achaar banayo chha me tuar kaaj ek barn bhejulo
par yo hamar khet aur jangal kaaj jaruri bhi to chha
dher paani piya ni to bimar hwe jala
sab phool phooli geyi basant sanch me aai go
ab we din bhar udham machalan
barkhaat me raat ke tyun ki awaj katuk jor hunchha
kuch logon ke u bhal laganchha par mero to muud pirane lag janchha
hao meri aama bhi yehi kunan chhi
aso lagan ro ki sanj tak pheri hyun padal
teen din bati eksaar paani padan ro mero jyu bhari hwe go
ham u lisa aag jalan lai jama kanan chhayi
we sidha saadha aur raji khushi wala din chhayi
me aam papad banan chhu garmi ki gham wek kaaj ekdam sahi chha
unke dekha hyunak manukh banan rayen
ab hamke har sanj bhunyun bhutta khanak milal
har saal pichla saal bati jada garam laganchha
mele hyun kaaj bado kath jama kari liyo
hao yo barkhaat aur wek bimariyon k ant ko prateek chha
hamke unar jaal me ni fasan chahano
bas kuch aur dinak baat chha fir pheri shanti hwe jaali
sarkari dawakhana ko daktar kabh ni milano
we kunechan ki we bado tej hunchhin aur jyu me garmi karchhin
meri chheli darati le kati ge ke lagaun
ghar ab bhoot walo jaso dikhano
hamar upjau jameen bekar huni
hamar chyul hi ek thul dawakhana chha
yo bhal chha ab tume money order ki baat ni dyekhan padani
yek kaaj ke karno chahano
kya koi bhi pradhan paani aur baatak thul janjal theek kari sako
tu hamesa meru saath rahulu?
deepawali ki badhai che!
